          "thoughts": [
            {
              "number": 1,
              "thought": "Voy a poblar patterns y decisions para 5 roles clave que cubran casos empresariales reales. Luego usaré model_add para crear relaciones entre entidades, y qa_ask para guardar Q&A corporativo. Finalmente documentaré todo en revision_210626/maquiavelic-plan.md. Patrones: (1) Budget forecast variance threshold pattern, (2) SOX compliance control pattern, (3) Tech debt prioritization pattern, (4) Multi-cloud failover pattern, (5) Q3 roadmap scoring pattern. Decisiones: (1) CFO decides between aggressive vs conservative forecasting, (2) CTO elige arquitectura multi-cloud vs single cloud, (3) Head of Product elige priorizar features vs tech debt.",
