        "maquiavelic-plan-tasks": {
          "thoughts": [
            {
              "number": 1,
              "thought": "Cada rol corporativo debe tener 2-3 tasks que representen sus planes de acción críticos. Voy a crear tasks que reflejen: (1) CFO - presupuesto Q3, auditoría SOX, cash flow optimization. (2) CTO - tech debt roadmap, cloud migration, security framework. (3) Head of Product - roadmap Q3, feedback synthesis, feature delivery. (4) Sales Director - enterprise pipeline, QBR prep, renewal forecast. (5) CMO - campaign Q3, attribution model, AB testing. (6) COO - process optimization, SLA review, vendor logistics. (7) CHRO - talent acquisition, performance review cycle, DEI metrics. (8) CISO - threat intel report, incident response drill, zero-trust rollout. (9) CIO - IT governance review, vendor contract renewal, helpdesk SLA. (10) Data Science - model retraining, feature pipeline, business insights deck. (11) QA Manager - test automation sprint, release validation. (12) DevOps Lead - CI/CD optimization, cost analysis. (13) Customer Success - onboarding Q3, NPS improvement. (14) Procurement - supplier negotiation Q3. (15) Legal - contract review, compliance mapping. (16) VP Engineering - hiring plan, technical roadmap. (17) Support Lead - ticket triage automation. (18) Partner Manager - co-selling Q3. (19) GRC - risk assessment Q3. (20) Infra Director - network availability, security patching.",
              "totalThoughts": 4,
              "nextThoughtNeeded": false,
